# id: RequestCallback -> void doWithRequest(ClientHttpRequest request) throws IOException_
commentText: Gets called by {@link RestTemplate#execute} with an opened {@code ClientHttpRequest}._Does not need to care about closing the request or about handling errors:_this will all be handled by the {@code RestTemplate}._@param request the active HTTP request_@throws IOException in case of I/O errors
